# Tungen, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Tungen () is a rural locality (an ulus) in Kurumkansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 41 as of 2010.
Geography
Tungen is located 53&nbsp;km east of Kurumkan (the district's administrative centre) by road. Arzgun is the nearest rural locality.
